snippet: Commissioner Rob Manfred put a time frame on the plan to play in Cuba by telling The Wall Street Journal that the most likely time to do it would be during spring training next year.
abstract: Baseball commissioner Rob Manfred says exhibition game with Cuba will likely take place during 2016 spring training season.
lead_paragraph: Commissioner Rob Manfred put a time frame on the plan to play in Cuba by telling The Wall Street Journal that the most likely time to do it would be during spring training next year.

headline.main: M.L.B. Exhibition Possible in Cuba Next Year
headline.print_headline: Exhibition Possible in Cuba Next Year
